      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_05_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "もうじき定期テストがあって……\nその勉強をしてたんです",
